{"tid":2301923,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–非洲大象每日流幾多汗水？","createTime":"2020-11-26T16:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T12:06:26.000Z","uid":38861,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"9062fc594fb5deae2ed81b3f3cbd80a771c1f751","tid":2301923,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:36:56.000Z","msg":"體型龐大的野外非洲大象(Loxodonta africana) ，每日步行接近8-12公里。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DPENztj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDPENztj.jpg&h=25d032b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在非洲的和暖氣候下，行走無可避免會出汗，那麼牠們每日大概會流失多少水份呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）有科學家利用動物園的非洲大象作研究(Ref1)，將D2O注入在麵包裡，讓大象吃下肚裡；<br />\n可以把D2O理解成為被標記的水份，從而可以區分本身沒有被標記的H2O水份。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yBUmDU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyBUmDU3.jpg&h=5718dd63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n讓D2O透過食物進入大象血液循環系統後，每隔24小時便會進行抽血動作，為期10日，透過量度D2O的流失量計算出水份流失率。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）最後計算得出，在攝氏25度中，大象每日水份的流失量約為身體重量的12%左右。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRrTu1M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRrTu1M.png&h=ae4e06df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基於是次研究對象為2000-5000kg的6隻大象，每日水份流失量的平均數為325升，最高可達516升。<br />\n<br />\n全球天氣逐漸極端化，野外大象將來能否從野外獲取足夠水份彌補所失水份，將成一大疑問。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=b075f623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://royalsocietypublishing.org/doi/pdf/10.1098/rsos.201155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Froyalsocietypublishing.org%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1098%2Frsos.201155&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=95a67ea4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://royalsocietypublishing.org/doi/pdf/10.1098/rsos.201155</a>"},{"pid":"baf4d6dc36d142126404c8e1a77c7d5e4ea13684","tid":2301923,"uid":380296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9062fc594fb5deae2ed81b3f3cbd80a771c1f751","tid":2301923,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:36:56.000Z","msg":"體型龐大的野外非洲大象(Loxodonta africana) ，每日步行接近8-12公里。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DPENztj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDPENztj.jpg&h=25d032b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在非洲的和暖氣候下，行走無可避免會出汗，那麼牠們每日大概會流失多少水份呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）有科學家利用動物園的非洲大象作研究(Ref1)，將D2O注入在麵包裡，讓大象吃下肚裡；<br />\n可以把D2O理解成為被標記的水份，從而可以區分本身沒有被標記的H2O水份。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yBUmDU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyBUmDU3.jpg&h=5718dd63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n讓D2O透過食物進入大象血液循環系統後，每隔24小時便會進行抽血動作，為期10日，透過量度D2O的流失量計算出水份流失率。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）最後計算得出，在攝氏25度中，大象每日水份的流失量約為身體重量的12%左右。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRrTu1M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRrTu1M.png&h=ae4e06df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基於是次研究對象為2000-5000kg的6隻大象，每日水份流失量的平均數為325升，最高可達516升。<br />\n<br />\n全球天氣逐漸極端化，野外大象將來能否從野外獲取足夠水份彌補所失水份，將成一大疑問。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=b075f623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://royalsocietypublishing.org/doi/pdf/10.1098/rsos.201155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Froyalsocietypublishing.org%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1098%2Frsos.201155&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=95a67ea4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://royalsocietypublishing.org/doi/pdf/10.1098/rsos.201155</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9a91e3142bf7bfc871c1d43b9c513b86829d86","tid":2301923,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:42:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30e782755b164b330a7a7bdd84e3fae6a8b16ad","tid":2301923,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:44:25.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e30c16654433a9de87bae06a0b8f5618ecfb44ab","tid":2301923,"uid":33749,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:45:46.000Z","msg":"聽男朋友講動物體積越大散熱就越慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁係大笨象咁大隻散熱咁慢<br />\n係唔係要靠出汗嚟幫助散熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac234e368f0b2e4484840051455c562a92b1d88e","tid":2301923,"uid":73855,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:46:01.000Z","msg":"喺邊有咁多水畀佢飲"},{"pid":"c5f6ad50105ea99f08b9e2c7150b48e1f57febd4","tid":2301923,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:47:14.000Z","msg":"象食麵包架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202950a8cbcace251e482e100ac95c21685bd78c","tid":2301923,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e30c16654433a9de87bae06a0b8f5618ecfb44ab","tid":2301923,"uid":33749,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:45:46.000Z","msg":"聽男朋友講動物體積越大散熱就越慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁係大笨象咁大隻散熱咁慢<br />\n係唔係要靠出汗嚟幫助散熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:47:48.000Z","msg":"出汗，排尿，可能仲有其他機制<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/aw